<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/parades-commission-for-northern-ireland> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Parades Commission for Northern Ireland (PCNI) is independent of government. It has the power to place restrictions on public processions and related protest meetings. PCNI is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Northern Ireland Office ."@en .
